documentation.description: Gets configuration and usage information about inference trained models.

model_id.description: The ID of the trained models stats to fetch

allow_no_match.description: Whether to ignore if a wildcard expression matches no trained models. (This includes `_all` string or when no trained models have been specified)

from.description: skips a number of trained models

size.description: specifies a max number of trained models to get

bytes.description: The unit in which to display byte values

format.description: a short version of the Accept header, e.g. json, yaml

h.description: Comma-separated list of column names to display

s.description: Comma-separated list of column names or column aliases to sort by

time.description: The unit in which to display time values
